Jo Prestia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo_Prestia 0 Jo Prestia (born 5 June 1960 in Porto Empedocle) is an Italian born French kick boxer and actor. He appeared in more than seventy films since 1996 and is best known for his performance as Le Tenia in Irréversible.
